author: Analysis by Chris Cillizza, CNN Editor-at-large
title: Analysis: Devin Nunes needs to stop talking about the coronavirus
description: On the same day that President Donald Trump acknowledged that somewhere between 100,000 and 200,000 Americans were likely to die because of the coronavirus, California Republican Rep. Devin Nunes went on Fox News to offer a very, uh, different perspective.
